  "2026-04-06T16:48:03.748Z",codex-agent,Duplicate-check evidence used pm context pm search and open or in-progress lists. Net-new scope under pm-o7be for calendar full-period contract clarity.
  "2026-04-06T18:25:49.246Z",codex-agent,"Implemented explicit period-boundary semantics for calendar day/week/month views with new --full-period (and --full_period alias) while preserving agenda behavior. Runtime now records both effective window and anchored period metadata in range payloads and markdown output clarifies period vs active-window wording. Contracts/completion/Pi parity updated so full-period appears in command flags, generated shell completion, and Pi calendar arguments. Validation includes unit coverage for day/week/month full-period behavior and rejection of --full-period on agenda view, plus release-readiness help/contract parity assertions."
